extendedInfo.description: This app has all the calculators you could need and more including amortization table for most calculators. Calculators: Auto Payment(Amort), Auto Affordability(Amort), Mortgage Payment(Amort), Mortgage Paydown(Amort), Interest, CD Maturity, Credit Card Payoff(Amort), Debt Payoff(Amort), Item Discount Price, Item Tax, Tip.
